						               													<description>Tar'Aram is a tactical game for 2-6 adventurers who try to find the secret access to the treasure chamber of the pyramid. Therefore century old mysteries have to be solved and obstacles must be cleared out of the way. But every adventurer should be faster than his opponents, because only the first will have access to the legendary treasury.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tar'Aram is a special game with unusual card-based game mechanics. The combination of race, tactical consideration and solving a mystery creates a unique feeling of playing. The playing field consists of several different parts, which is why the game board can be combined individually.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is aimed at players aged 10 and over, who have fun in tactics and deduction games. The rules are learned quickly, the game itself is attractive by its many possibilities for both casual and multi-player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The name is composed of arabic tariq = way and aharam = pyramid, by the way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
